channel.title: Get a Free Domain! Easy!
channel.description:
I figured I'd post this, considering lots of people create websites here,
All you have to do is gain 7 points from either filling out a few surveys, or just registering an account and verifying it by email. Don't just say you've completed a form when you haven't, they manually check to see if you actually did it. After you have received 7 points, you can request your domain, a .com, .net, w/e, and they will register it for you within 24 hours! Its a great service, and hope this helps!
Note: I don't get any cash unless you get your domain, so realize I wouldn't support this if it did not work! Thanks!
[url=http://www.dietzel.com/partner/idevaffiliate.php?id=362]http://www.dietzel.com/partner/idevaffiliate.php?id=362[/url]
That is my referral link, so if you are planning on registering, please use my link so I can make 2 bucks, I'm currently in debt in paypal thanks to a chargeback :/
~Jewsus~
